
  To get a registered account, send mail to nash@visus.com with the
following information:
1. You desired account name. This should be at least 3 alphabetical
   characters. No punctuation!
2. Your real name.
3. Your email address.

A line like this would be very nice for the administrator:
fics_addplayer red "Richard Nash" nash@visus.com

  Of course, substitute your own information for the above.
